<article id="post-348" class="post-348 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-general category-travel tag-air-canada tag-alberta tag-british-columbia tag-calgary tag-japan tag-kelowna tag-vancouver tag-westjet">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2004/04/turning-japanese-again-yotsukaido-calgary/" rel="bookmark">Turning Japanese Again, Returning to Canada</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>I can&#8217;t even call this a &#8220;last day&#8221;. Yesterday, really, was our last day. Today is the packing/travelling day.<br />
And the day to say goodbye to dear friends. I hate leaving friends behind.<br />
 <a href="http://geoff.wp/2004/04/turning-japanese-again-yotsukaido-calgary/#more-348" class="more-link">Continue reading<span class="screen-reader-text"> &#8220;Turning Japanese Again, Returning to Canada&#8221;</span></a></p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	<footer class="entry-footer">
